  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many women also later when some young women had been coming to the farm to his family also a young man is here, might as well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always stand at a distance because I couldn't afford to reveal that I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, very many women because I was a city boy not a farm boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also to the one younger woman at the young farmer and helped me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, there was one doctor over there which I became a very close friend because the only intelligencia out there was myself, a doctor, and a federal administrator of the-- with his family, and forester also, very intelligent man because he was studying forestry.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're like click.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But was one doctor which I was coming to his house, and he has a library.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I naturally always go and look in the books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was looking in the books because I heard that there are occasions where a man either has a some disease or some infection and has to be circumcised.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't call it circumcising, I call it surgery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- so I look at the books and study and I studied effects under what circumstances, and in my mind I established a story.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you could-- you could wake me up during the night or under any conditions, and I will know the story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You would ask me to repeat 100 times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I knew exactly is that I had such infection and I have so many medication.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nothing helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was operated in such and such hospital by such, such doctor, at such and such time, and there were so many days in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I know the story forwards and backwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
